---
// src/pages/services/fireplace-repair.astro
// GSC cluster: 1,500+ impressions/quarter
// "fireplace repair" 258 imp pos 11.5, almost top-10 without page
// "fireplace repair los angeles" 217 imp pos 28.6
// "gas fireplace repair los angeles" 142 imp pos 28.6
